-- Piguet Galland Appoints BCV’s Gerard Haeberli as New Chairman
-- B y   S i m e o n   B e n n e t t
-- 2012-05-01T07:40:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-01/piguet-galland-appoints-bcv-s-gerard-haeberli-as-new-chairman.html
Swiss private bank Piguet Galland &
Cie SA proposed Gerard Haeberli, head of private banking at
Piguet’s parent company,  Banque Cantonale Vaudoise (BCVN) , as chairman.  Piguet also proposed Thomas W. Paulsen, BCV’s chief
financial officer, for the board, it said in an e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Simeon Bennett in Geneva at 
 sbennett9@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
